# Timeline

Chronological list of events.

## Basic Usage
::TuffDemo{title="Timeline" description="Highlight recent updates." code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxTimeline>
      <TxTimelineItem title="Design phase" time="09:30" color="primary" />
      <TxTimelineItem title="Build" time="12:00" color="success" />
      <TxTimelineItem title="Launch" time="16:10" color="warning" />
    </TxTimeline>
  </template>
---
#preview
<tx-timeline>
  <tx-timeline-item title="Design phase" time="09:30" color="primary" />
  <tx-timeline-item title="Build" time="12:00" color="success" />
  <tx-timeline-item title="Launch" time="16:10" color="warning" />
</tx-timeline>
:::

## API (Lite)
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: layout
